title: Season 1-3 Texture Packs - Help me
body:
Hello , i like all the skins , sprites and texture pack that were used before, if anyone knows how to replace the new files with the old ones, im paying him.
Or just help me for free please.

replies.body: Old map or texture skins aren't available, and we don't support modifications or third party programs that may suggest it.  Check out our [third party guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/225266848), and stay safe!
